minimal arch linux desktop
--------------------------

hyprland, kitty, zsh, waybar, rofi, dunst, and small helpers.

setup
-----

    git clone <repository-url> ~/Dev/dotfiles
    cd ~/Dev/dotfiles
    ./install.sh --dry-run
    ./install.sh

packages
--------

core: hyprland kitty zsh uwsm fzf eza
desktop: waybar rofi dunst
optional: bluetooth clipboard power screenshots

configs
-------

    config/hypr/       hyprland
    config/kitty/      kitty
    config/zsh/        zsh
    config/waybar/     waybar
    config/rofi/       rofi
    config/dunst/      dunst
    config/wlogout/    wlogout
    bin/               helper scripts

machine monitor
---------------

    cp local/hypr/local.conf.example ~/.config/hypr/local.conf

updates
-------

    git pull
    ./scripts/verify.sh repository
    ./install.sh

rollback
--------

    ./scripts/restore.sh ~/.local/state/dotfiles/backups/<timestamp>
